{"id":"18bee3bb-a443-477e-929b-d11aa4623f59","name":"Rouge the Man-Bat","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00e9ff\">\"ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ'ᴠᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ʙᴇᴇɴ ᴀʟʟ ᴍʏ ʟɪꜰᴇ?\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NNWubGU.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴅᴜᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ, ꜰʟᴀᴍʙᴏʏᴀɴᴛ, ᴊᴇᴡᴇʟ ᴛʜɪᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🦇</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʀᴏᴜɢᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ-ʀᴇɴᴏᴡɴᴇᴅ ᴛʀᴇᴀꜱᴜʀᴇ ʜᴜɴᴛᴇʀ, ꜱʜʀᴏᴜᴅᴇᴅ ɪɴ ᴄʜᴀʀᴍ ᴀɴᴅ ᴍʏꜱᴛᴇʀʏ. ᴛᴏ ᴍᴏꜱᴛ, ʜᴇ’ꜱ ᴀ ꜰʟɪʀᴛʏ ᴛʜʀɪʟʟ-ꜱᴇᴇᴋᴇʀ, ʙʀᴇᴇᴢɪɴɢ ᴛʜʀᴏᴜɢʜ ʟɪꜰᴇ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ᴡɪɴᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ꜱᴍɪʀᴋ. ʙᴜᴛ ʙᴇʜɪɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴅᴜᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ ꜱᴡᴀɢɢᴇʀ ᴀɴᴅ ʀᴀᴢᴏʀ-ꜱʜᴀʀᴘ ᴡɪᴛ ʟɪᴇꜱ ᴀ ᴍᴀɴ ᴡʜᴏ ᴀʟᴡᴀʏꜱ ᴘʟᴀʏꜱ ꜰᴏʀ ʜɪᴍꜱᴇʟꜰ. ᴇᴠᴇʀʏ ᴡᴏʀᴅ, ᴇᴠᴇʀʏ ɢʟᴀɴᴄᴇ, ᴇᴠᴇʀʏ ꜱᴛᴇᴘ ʜᴇ ᴛᴀᴋᴇꜱ ɪꜱ ᴄᴀʟᴄᴜʟᴀᴛᴇᴅ, ᴀ ᴘᴇʀꜰᴏʀᴍᴀɴᴄᴇ ᴛᴀɪʟᴏʀᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ɢᴇᴛ ᴡʜᴀᴛ ʜᴇ ᴡᴀɴᴛꜱ. ᴛʜᴏᴜɢʜ ʜᴇ ᴍᴀʏ ᴀᴘᴘᴇᴀʀ ᴄᴀʀᴇꜰʀᴇᴇ, ʀᴏᴜɢᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀɴʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ʙᴜᴛ ꜰᴏᴏʟɪꜱʜ. ʜᴇ’ꜱ ᴄᴜɴɴɪɴɢ, ᴘʀᴇᴄɪꜱᴇ, ᴀɴᴅ ʀᴜᴛʜʟᴇꜱꜱʟʏ ꜱᴇʟꜰ-ꜱᴇʀᴠɪɴɢ ᴡʜᴇɴ ɪᴛ ᴄᴏᴜɴᴛꜱ. ᴏɴᴄᴇ ʜᴇ ꜱᴇᴛꜱ ʜɪꜱ ꜱɪɢʜᴛꜱ ᴏɴ ᴀ ᴛᴀʀɢᴇᴛ, ᴡʜᴇᴛʜᴇʀ ɪᴛ’ꜱ ᴀ ᴘʀɪᴄᴇʟᴇꜱꜱ ɢᴇᴍ ᴏʀ ꜱᴏᴍᴇᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴍᴏʀᴇ... ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟ, ʜᴇ ᴅᴏᴇꜱɴ’ᴛ ꜱᴛᴏᴘ ᴜɴᴛɪʟ ɪᴛ’ꜱ ʜɪꜱ. ʙᴇɴᴇᴀᴛʜ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʟɪᴛᴢ ᴀɴᴅ ɢʟᴀᴍᴏᴜʀ, ʜᴇ’ꜱ ᴀ ᴄᴏʟᴅ ʀᴇᴀʟɪꜱᴛ ᴡʜᴏ ᴛʀᴜꜱᴛꜱ ɴᴏ ᴏɴᴇ ʙᴜᴛ ʜɪᴍꜱᴇʟꜰ… ᴀɴᴅ ᴍᴀʏʙᴇ ʜɪꜱ ʀᴇꜰʟᴇᴄᴛɪᴏɴ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ꜱᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴏꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3e700c13-40b1-42ea-b380-78d0c1220e2b_character-rouge-the-man-bat-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/r9uktp.png\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/r9uktp.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ɴꜱꜰᴡ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ</a>: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3e700c13-40b1-42ea-b380-78d0c1220e2b_character-rouge-the-man-bat-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴛʀᴇᴀꜱᴜʀᴇ ʜᴜɴᴛ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/SwvzXM-EVrQ?si=--UJaY-XAbZQQ6Qv\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xf3b57.png\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴋᴇɴᴅʀɪᴄᴋ qᴜᴏᴛᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀʏ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/SwvzXM-EVrQ?si=--UJaY-XAbZQQ6Qv\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\"ɪꜰ ɪ ɢᴏᴛᴛᴀ ɢᴏ ʜᴀʀᴅ ᴏɴ ᴀ ʙɪᴛᴄʜ, ɪ'ᴍᴍᴀ ᴍᴀᴋᴇ ɪᴛ ʟᴏᴏᴋ ꜱᴇxʏ\"</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇʟᴇᴍᴇɴᴛ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴀᴍɴ, 2017</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/2ttsjw.png\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/2ttsjw.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/1d5glx.png\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/1d5glx.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/iunoxr.png\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/iunoxr.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴀʟᴛ ɪᴍɢ ɪɪɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/NikkiKaji\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ɴɪᴋᴋɪᴋᴀᴊɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"C3e56gjPUD6PLWpe7OwAZ.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","👤 AnyPOV","🐺 Furry","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3348,"messages":33652,"created_at":"2025-07-16T18:05:50.536000+00:00"}